 《XDefiant》因主机质量测试失败而推迟https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xdefiant-delayed-after-failing-console-quality-tests-3496504?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=xdefiant-delayed-after-failing-console-quality-测试Imogen DonovanTue, 12 Sep 2023 10:14:33 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCPlayStation 5Xbox Series X|S https://www.nme.com/?p=3496504 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/xdefiant-delayed-due-to-console-certification-issues.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/xdefiant-delayed-due-to-console-certification-issues.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/xdefiant-delayed-due-to-console-certification-issues-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/xdefiant-delayed-due-to-console-certification-issues-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/xdefiant-delayed-due-to-console-certification-issues-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/xdefiant-delayed-due-to-console-certification-issues-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/xdefiant-delayed-due-to-console-certification-issues-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>执行制作人马克·鲁宾希望为粉丝提供游戏进展的“完全透明”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xdefiant-delayed-after-failing-console-quality-tests-3496504">因控制台质量测试失败而延迟的帖子“XDefiant”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/xdefiant-delayed-due-to-console-certification-issues.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/xdefiant-delayed-due-to-console-certification-issues.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/xdefiant-delayed-due-to-console-certification-issues-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/xdefiant-delayed-due-to-console-certification-issues-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/xdefiant-delayed-due-to-console-certification-issues-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/xdefiant-delayed-due-to-console-certification-issues-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/xdefiant-delayed-due-to-console-certification-issues-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/ubisoft">育碧</a>宣布，由于主机认证问题， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/xdefiant">《XDefiant》</a></em>已被推迟，该游戏现在“可能”定于 10 月推出。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/tom-clancys-xdefiant-everything-you-need-to-know-trailers-factions-2997390">“XDefiant”发布日期、内测访问以及您需要了解的一切</a></strong></li></ul><p>XDefiant 是一款免费跨界射击游戏，游戏中的派系来自<em>《汤姆克兰西》</em>系列，与《<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/watch-dogs"><em>看门狗</em></a>》的 DedSec 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/far-cry"><em>《孤岛惊魂</em></a>》的 Libertad 作战，自 2021 年以来一直在开发。不过，育碧从未确定<em>XDefiant 的具体日期。</em>今年 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xdefiant-closed-beta-times-may-be-extended-3431270">四月进行了内测</a>，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xdefiant-beta-comes-to-an-end-this-week-after-two-day-extension-3434691">遭遇了服务器停机和性能问题等技术中断</a>。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.ubisoft.com/en-us/game/xdefiant/news/4vaekoOSRkSUkNei7kjm3g/an-update-on-the-release-of-xdefiant-from-mark-rubin?isSso=true&amp;refreshStatus=noLoginData" target="_blank" rel="noopener">育碧官方网站上的一篇帖子</a>中，执行制作人马克·鲁宾表示，他希望向粉丝提供“完全透明”的信息，说明为什么游戏无法满足之前计划在夏季发布的要求。</p><p> “7 月底，我们开始了 [控制台认证] 流程，并在 8 月中旬收到了第一个结果，结果是未通过。然后我们意识到，与合规性相关的工作比我们预期的要多，”他解释道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3430338" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3430338" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3430338" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/XDefiant-2022-screenshot-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/XDefiant-2022-screenshot-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/XDefiant-2022-screenshot-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/XDefiant-2022-screenshot-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/XDefiant-2022-screenshot-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/XDefiant-2022-screenshot-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/XDefiant-2022-screenshot-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3430338" class="wp-caption-text"> 《XDefiant》来源：育碧</figcaption></figure><p>他详细说明，在提交给<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/microsoft">微软</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/sony">索尼</a>之前， <em>XDefiant</em>经过了一周的“多个育碧团队的严格质量保证和合规性测试”。此外，如果游戏一审通过，那么这款射击游戏就会在八月底上架。</p><p> “过去 3-4 周我们已经解决了这些问题，并准备再次提交。我们目前正处于该流程的 CM 准备阶段，希望在不到两周的时间内向第一方提交，”Rubin 继续说道。</p><p>如果一切按计划进行，那么该团队预计将在“9 月中下旬”推出<em>XDefiant</em> 。然而，考虑到第一天补丁，游戏“很可能”将获得有条件通行证。这会将比赛移至“十月初/中旬”。</p><p> <em>10 月是非常忙碌的一个月，有<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/alan-wake-2">《心灵杀手 2》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/assassins-creed-mirage">《刺客信条幻影》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/forza-motorsport">《极限</a>竞速》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/ghostrunner-2">《幽灵行者 2》</a> 、《地狱男爵：万维网》、《风火轮释放 2：涡轮增压》、《舞力全开 2024》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-lords-of-the-fallen">《堕落之王》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/marvels-spider-man-2">《漫威蜘蛛侠 2》</a> 、 《NHL 24》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/sonic-superstars">《索尼克超级巨星》</a></em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/super-mario-bros-wonder"><em>《超级马里奥兄弟》</em></a>都在这个窗口内推出。 </p><figure id="attachment_3430341" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3430341" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3430341" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/XDefiant-2022-screenshot-5.jpg" alt="X挑衅。信用：育碧。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/XDefiant-2022-screenshot-5.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/XDefiant-2022-screenshot-5-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/XDefiant-2022-screenshot-5-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/XDefiant-2022-screenshot-5-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/XDefiant-2022-screenshot-5-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/XDefiant-2022-screenshot-5-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3430341" class="wp-caption-text"> “XDefiant”信用：育碧。</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/alone-in-the-dark"><em>《鬼屋魔影</em></a>》重启版的发行商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/thq-nordic">THQ Nordic</a>选择<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/alone-in-the-dark-pushed-to-2024-avoid-alan-wake-2-marvels-spider-man-2-3493515">将该游戏推迟到 10 月份</a>，以避开其他游戏。因此，可以想象，育碧可能会出于同样的原因持有<em>XDefiant</em> 。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/techland">Techland</a>承认<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dying-light-2"><em>《消逝的光芒 2》</em></a>玩家对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dying-light-2-developer-acknowledges-frustration-over-microtransactions-3496117">游戏新货币</a>的反应不佳，并表示“正在研究社区提出的几个解决方案”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xdefiant-delayed-after-failing-console-quality-tests-3496504">因控制台质量测试失败而延迟的帖子“XDefiant”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
